5>Returns:</h5><p>Promise resolving to base64 data URI string</p>\n<h5>Throws:</h5><p>When GM stream is invalid or format conversion fails</p>\n<h5>Example:</h5><pre><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"pl-c\">// Convert to base64 JPEG (default)</span>\n<span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> { <span class=\"pl-c1\">gmStream</span> } <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">await</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">getGmStream</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>./images<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>, <span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>photo.jpg<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>);\n<span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">dataUri</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">await</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">toBase64</span>(<span class=\"pl-smi\">gmStream</span>);\n<span class=\"pl-c\">// Returns: \"data:image/jpg;base64,/9j/4AAQSkZJRgABAQAAAQ...\"</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h5>Example:</h5><pre><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"pl-c\">// Convert to base64 PNG for transparency support</span>\n<span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">pngDataUri</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">await</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">toBase64</span>(<span class=\"pl-smi\">gmStream</span>, <span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>png<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>);\n<span class=\"pl-c1\">document</span>.<span class=\"pl-c1\">getElementById</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>img<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>).<span class=\"pl-smi\">src</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\">pngDataUri</span>;\n</code></pre>\n<h5>Example:</h5><pre><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"pl-c\">// Convert processed image to base64 for CSS background</span>\n<span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">resized</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">resizeImg</span>(<span class=\"pl-s